Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人は生まれながら光と影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:13.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光と影を纏い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Their only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:25.14,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}欲しいもの全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:29.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手に入れること
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:36.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}それが幸せなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:41.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}誰かが笑顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:47.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どこかできっと泣いてる人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:59.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}すれ違うほど　愛おしく思う気持ちがある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ひとときのあいだに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:10.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕らはみんな矛盾を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:18.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あしたへの光を見つめながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}歩いてくのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:02.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人类从出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:13.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就一直缠绕着光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:25.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将一切想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:29.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}都收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:36.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那真的就幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:41.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果有人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:47.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那一定在某处也有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:59.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}每当擦肩而过 就会觉得怜爱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在转瞬而逝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:10.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们都会怀抱着矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:18.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够一直看着通向明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一直走下去吗
