Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 我会一直相信栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起相信她 等她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕具座之门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周已经3次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意的话 就到邮件里写的地点来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创太多 没衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把恶灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这打扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正缠创后都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就选了不需要的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用福利挽救收视率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是有这种难以启齿的原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 赶紧变完身到现场去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是衰弱事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周已经发生3起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且又是退魔少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不是你们普通人能应付的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能全甩给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻真是的 又放莫名其妙的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了向世人推广退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越熟练了 不过不太明显就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克这么说 我就有信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持这个势头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 我们趁早回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么小克 再发生案件时请联系我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让那几个孩子参加战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初 我推断奈兹的目的是皇缠的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在感觉他们的目的变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海边发生的案件也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是有预谋发动进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意在探清皇缠她们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弄清楚奈兹的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也得把他们放在最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直让小喽啰出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特究竟在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我们出手 一两个小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不要小瞧的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些小丫头可是打败了菲戈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说「切不可大意」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用着急 赛特很快就会给我们指示的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟就是为了这个才叫我们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过路过千万不要错过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2000日元卖给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积攒的零花钱和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼职巫女赚的钱一共是8400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少得用这笔钱再买10件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我的衣服就真不够穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很可爱 虽然很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮她付了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你做这点事总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说给你添麻烦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉你买的都是又朴素又便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为都打算只在家里穿穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你已经帮我买了件好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 你不用去上班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有退魔少女在大显身手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事让波奇做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得今天不用上班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟忙碌的刑警也需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要变热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说今天也是30℃以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没话说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 赛特指定的人好像是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被丢下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰面的地方真的是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然叫我们过来所为何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创后的克拉露丝被目击过好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不宜再待在街区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于奈兹的出现频率和出现地点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和IATO共享情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对于 我没有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们到里面详谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要去里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从不开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事都要讲究先后顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是顺序来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝也在里面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你能来 吾妻大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾妻大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾妻大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿杏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海神社发生的事已经都写在报告里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想亲口问问统领海之巫女的…阿杏你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道她或许能够打开超次元之门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候告诉她栞的事 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必知道真相后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠会不顾后果地采取行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她性格率直 和栞一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着在这种地方吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太浪费钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是暑假 却没有客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里撑得下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就好好享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 退后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把她送到塔外去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是先逃离这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 那个女人是恶灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特真是的 尽提些难为人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是恶灵干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐被冻住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那间旅馆是那种场所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 请宽恕罪孽深重的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然没人报警
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声明意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DR反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把我们怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么手机在这么高的地方打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 冻住了 打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温度也在不断下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过高次元空间逃出去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围不仅有冰 还笼罩着看不见的恶灵力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用我的能力试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤出神灵的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 被恶灵的屏障阻挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(960,985)}Photogenic Plasma Illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超美少女等离子幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走高次元空间去现场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然布下了次元防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就强行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 由麻的攻击竟然无效
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈兹的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从高次元空间也无法进入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到了望台里的情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面似乎温度极低 估计在零度以下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 今天缠去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是有预谋发动的进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说今天要和她爸爸去釜谷公园的跳蚤市场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠和皇巡查部长在了望塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 身体已经冷得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿成那样 难道不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说退魔少女的能力可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看这边 转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对 绝对不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事 以前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不许看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能倒在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要和女儿一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等妻子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这样下去 伸吾君就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在了望台确认到皇缠的身影
